    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 供应商 CLN 要求银行减记 90% 的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/stellantis-supplier-cln-asks-banks-to-take-90-writedown-on-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利汽车零部件制造商 CLN-Coils Lamiere Nastri SpA 要求银行债权人减记约 90% 的无担保贷款，以期在汽车行业危机期间大幅减少债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/stellantis-supplier-cln-asks-banks-to-take-90-writedown-on-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 09:54:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PJT 与新世界债券持有人举行电话会议讨论贷款事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/pjt-holds-call-with-new-world-bondholders-on-loan-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，债务顾问 PJT Partners Inc. 周四与新世界发展有限公司的部分美元债券持有人举行了电话会议，讨论这家陷入困境的开发商正在进行的贷款谈判是否最终可能导致其债券违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/pjt-holds-call-with-new-world-bondholders-on-loan-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 09:42:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Recruit Holdings 首席执行官谈论人工智能劳动力和并购前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-23/recruit-holdings-ceo-talks-ai-workforce-m-a-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Recruit Holdings 首席执行官 Hisayuki “Deko” Idekoba 在达沃斯接受彭博电视台 Haslinda Amin 采访时，分享了对人工智能与就业和劳动力市场以及公司并购机会的看法。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
